            "title": "Scorpio Tankers Inc. Announces Pricing of Convertible Senior Notes due 2031 and Concurrent Stock Repurchase",
            "id": "af88d7fa-5d6d-4936-9b9e-59d323f7ced3",
            "description": "Scorpio Tankers Inc. (NYSE: STNG) revealed today that it has priced a private offering of $325 million in 1.75% convertible senior notes due 2031, which is an increase from the initially announced $300 million. The Notes are solely available to qualified institutional buyers under Rule 144A of the Securities Act of 1933. Additionally, the Company has given the initial purchasers the option to acquire up to an extra $50 million in Notes within a 13-day period from the issuance date.",
